There are lots of notepads for Android. But this one is better.

----------------------------------------------------------------

Current features

  - Notes

  - Labels with names and colors

  - Navigation


Planned features

  - Export/Import using external storage

  - Sync with cloud service (Dropbox or another)

  - Archive old notes

  - Notes/Labels search with suggest


----------------------------------------------------------------

Application core is in the <project>/app directory.
Just use Gradle to build. Gradle Wrapper provided.